ical future-noir fable drenched in the heady perfume of death, Blade Runner is returning to cinema screens 33 years after its troubled birth. \r\n\r\nThe tale of grizzled bounty hunter Rick Deckard and his mission to execute a mutinous gang of replicants – synthetic biological androids who are barely distinguishable from humans – Ridley Scott’s third film remains his most beloved and richly layered work. But does it still hold up decades later? And what can Blade Runner tell us about technology, politics, architecture, life, death and the human condition in 2015?","created":"2015-04-08T00:00:00.000Z"},{"uuid":"fcb30ad9-15cb-4204-bddc-74246af4cef9","title":"The Best Sci-Fi Characters of All Time: the verdict","url":"https://www.bfi.org.uk/news/best-sci-fi-characters-all-time-verdict","image":{"src":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-08/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg/960x540-cropped/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg","thumbnail":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-08/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg/960x540-cropped/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg","preload":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-08/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg/96x54-cropped/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg","sidebar":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-08/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg/480x720-cropped/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg","sidebarPreload":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-08/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg/48x72-cropped/doctor-who-50th-anniversary-composite.jpg","alt":null},"category":"","authors":[],"type":"News","sourceCms":"core-cms","summary":"Ellen Ripley and the Doctor went head to head. The votes have now been counted.","created":"2014-12-17T00:00:00.000Z"},{"uuid":"ddf02c45-d6ed-4b